About this item

  • Analog-Digital Dual Display – The SKMEI Model 2020 Digital Watch combines classic analog style with a digital interface for maximum functionality. Ideal for work, sports, and Dialy use.
  • Multi-Functional Watch – Features chronograph stopwatch, alarm, three time zones, date & week display, 12/24 hour format, and EL backlight for easy night-time viewing.
  • Durable & Stylish Build – Made with a polycarbonate (PC) case and leather band, this leather band watch is lightweight (87.9g) and comfortable for all-day wear.
  • Waterproof Digital Watch – With 30M water resistance, this men’s digital watch is safe from splashes, rain, and sweat, making it great for outdoor adventures and Dialy use.
  • Versatile & Trendy Design – Available in multiple stylish colors, including Amber Transparent, Blue Transparent, Pink Transparent, White Transparent, Silver/Black, and Black/Brown to match any outfit.

How are ratings calculated?
